meanings.definition: To surpass in bidding at an auction.
meanings.sent1: She always outbidders everyone at the auction.
meanings.sent2: He outbidders his competitors with higher bids.
meanings.sent3: The sneaky fox outbidders the other animals for the juiciest fruits.
meanings.sent4: Her determination to outbidders the rest shines through in every auction.
meanings.sent5: Outbidders like her make auctions exciting and competitive.
